data.description: Step into this well maintained home across from the beautiful McKenzie River and enjoy the spacious room for indoor and outdoor gatherings. Kitchen boasts an abundance of storage and counter space. This half acre property features an extra deep garage with workshop, plenty of room or your RV or boat under covered storage, and a greenhouse to start your garden in the spacious yard filled with fruit trees and grapes. Fresh bark dust in front yard. New roof in 2020.
